Do you have a request or a bug? Let me know here:
A private room is a special room that does [u]not appear on the active rooms list[/u]. They are effective for preventing against trolls, just make sure that the room name is complicated to guess!
How often do you release updates?
I try to release new updates bi-monthly. However, I will make more updates if I have increased demand for a specific feature or if there is a major bug I need to address.

If you want to reach me about anything, I will usually be on the main room around 5 PM CT. (Not a guarantee!). You can also submit a google form for comments, questions, bugs, requests, or anything (Just don't spam it please).

If someone is asking you for personal information that you feel uncomfortable sharing, don't share it. Here it is extremely easy to be anonymous. Remember that you have the ability to leave the chat room at any time or kick them off if you are the host. Private rooms exist too.
How does the chat room work?

If you try to join a room that does not exist in the active rooms list, a new room will be created with you as the host. If the host leaves that chat room, everyone else is kicked off also. (I'm working to fix this issue)
